properties.name: groupId
properties.description: Identifying this action bar item belongs to a certain group and should only be shown once.
properties.rawdescription: Identifying this action bar item belongs to a certain group and should only be shown once.

properties.name: inGroupPriority
properties.description: If action bar items has the same groupId, only one is displayed. Action bar item with the same groupId that has highest inGroupPriority is displayed.
properties.rawdescription:
If action bar items has the same groupId, only one is displayed.
Action bar item with the same groupId that has highest inGroupPriority is displayed.

properties.name: injector
properties.description: The injector to use. If not set, the default root injector will be used.
properties.rawdescription: The injector to use. If not set, the default root injector will be used.

properties.name: placement
properties.description: The placement of the item. more is a dropdown on the right side.
properties.rawdescription:
The placement of the item. `more` is a dropdown
on the right side.

properties.name: priority
properties.rawdescription: Ordering of the actions (high number first)
